title: 'The Bachelor' Villain Corinne Calls Vanessa 'Lucky Bitch' and Feels Bloated | TMZ.com
text:
'The Bachelor' Villain Corinne Calls Vanessa 'Lucky Bitch' and Feels Bloated 'Bachelor' Corinne Vanessa's a 'Lucky Bitch' ... And I'm Super Bloated 1 2/13/2017 6:21 PM PST 
Corinne hasn't had a 1-on-1 date with Nick Viall yet, so she was sure she was going to get one tonight on "The Bachelor" ... but it didn't happen ... and she was pissed. 
Usually when a girl calls another girl a "lucky bitch," she's playing around ... but Corinne -- who's embraced the villain role -- didn't even crack a smile after Vanessa scored the exclusive date instead of her. 
Corinne let out her full frustration ... along with a bloated grunt that's sure to make the show's future lowlight reel.
